6.Discussion
Theresultsofthispaperhavebroadimplicationsfordeterminations
of
i
basedonmod-
elingofellipsoidallightcurves.ThestatechangeswehavefoundinA0
620arelikelypresent
 {34{
inmanyoralloftheothersevenblackholebinarieswithperiodslessth
