Figure5showsthateventhecurveswhichlackconspicuousnonellips
oidalfeaturesare
besttwithsignicantvariationinthedisk.Therearetwotypesofd
isklightcurves:
oneslikeV6,I6,andI8whichareroughlysinusoidal,andoneslikeW2,W
