Thesinusoidalanddouble-waveddiskcurvesareeasilyunderstood
inthecontextof
ELC'sdiskmodel.Allmodelsincludeasinglespotontherim,extendingpa
rtwaydown
thefaceofthedisk;therelativeimportanceoftheface(sinusoida
l)andrim(secondpeak)
